'''威廉·詹姆斯·隆巴帝'''（William James Lombardy，{{bd|1937年|12月4日|2017年|10月13日|catIdx=Lombardy}}），[[美国|美国]][[国际象棋|国际象棋]]棋手、国际象棋理论家。1960年获[[国际象棋特级大师|国际象棋特级大师]]称号。

隆巴帝是1950、1960年代美国最杰出的棋手之一，曾担任过[[鲍比·菲舍尔|鲍比·菲舍尔]]的教练。1960年，他带领美国队夺得在[[列宁格勒|列宁格勒]]举行的世界国际象棋学生团体锦标赛冠军。<ref>Edmonds & Eidinow 2004, p. 43.</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.olimpbase.org/index.html?http%3A%2F%2Fwww.olimpbase.org%2Fyouth%2Fstud_handbook.html |title=World Student Team Chess Championship summary |year=2013 |publisher=OlimpBase |accessdate=September 7, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161029044332/http://www.olimpbase.org/index.html?http%3A%2F%2Fwww.olimpbase.org%2Fyouth%2Fstud_handbook.html |archive-date=2016-10-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>他还是1957年[[世界青年国际象棋锦标赛|世界青年冠军]]，并且是该赛事历史上唯一以满分夺冠的棋手。<ref>Kažić 1974, p. pp. 273-74</ref><ref>Lombardy 2011, p. 66.</ref>

2017年10月13日週五，隆巴帝因突發性[[心肌梗死|心肌梗死]]，於[[馬丁尼茲_(加利福尼亞州)|馬丁尼茲]]的好友拉斐爾·帕爾米耶里（{{lang|en|Ralph Palmieri}}）家中過世<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://en.chessbase.com/post/william-lombardy-1937-2017 |title=Chessbase: RIP 'Father Bill' |access-date=2017-12-15 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116040303/https://en.chessbase.com/post/william-lombardy-1937-2017 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/14/obituaries/william-lombardy-dead-chess-grandmaster.html |title=''The New York Times'': William Lombardy, Chess Grandmaster Turned Priest, Dies at 79 |accessdate=2017-12-15 |archive-date=2017-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171016084048/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/14/obituaries/william-lombardy-dead-chess-grandmaster.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2017/oct/17/father-bill-lombardy-bobby-fischers-great-contempo/ |title=Washington Times: ‘Father Bill’ Lombardy, Bobby Fischer’s great contemporary, dies at 79 |access-date=2017-12-15 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030526/https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2017/oct/17/father-bill-lombardy-bobby-fischers-great-contempo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.irishtimes.com/sport/chess-the-church-and-the-cold-war-the-life-of-fr-bill-lombardy-1.3260707 |title=The Irish Times: Chess, the church and the Cold War: The life of Fr Bill Lombardy |access-date=2017-12-15 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019222234/http://www.irishtimes.com/sport/chess-the-church-and-the-cold-war-the-life-of-fr-bill-lombardy-1.3260707 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2017/oct/20/william-lombardy-exceptional-performance-often-overlooked |title=The Guardian: William Lombardy’s exceptional performance in 1960 is often overlooked |access-date=2017-12-15 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web